        "Title": "Fly Me to the Moonraker",
        "Description": "&quot;I&apos;d heard Gabrielli Monaco is obsessed with the conquest of space. I don&apos;t believe it.&quot;\r\r[ROCKET FUEL ENGAGE.]\r\r&quot;Let him fly amongst the stars!&quot;\r\r[CHAIN REACTION SEQUENCE SPOTTED, NOW SENDING SPACE-LOVER TO THE MOON.]\r\r&quot;. . .&quot;\r\r&quot;. . . Now I can believe it.&quot;\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Ashley.",
